#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.combine_first.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.combine\\_first"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:1 of
msgid "Update null elements with value in the same location in 'other'."
msgstr "使用 'other' 中相同位置的值更新空元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:3 of
msgid ""
"Combine two Series objects by filling null values in one Series with non-"
"null values from the other Series. Result index will be the union of the "
"two indexes."
msgstr ""
"通过用另一个 Series 中的非空值填充一个 Series 中的空值来合并两个 Series "
"对象。结果索引将是两个索引的并集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:7 of
msgid "The value(s) to be used for filling null values."
msgstr "用于填充空值的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:10 of
msgid "The result of combining the provided Series with the other object."
msgstr "将提供的 Series 与另一个对象合并的结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:15 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.combine`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:16 of
msgid "Perform element-wise operation on two Series using a given function."
msgstr "使用给定函数对两个 Series 执行逐元素操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:19 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine_first.series_combine_first:30 of
msgid ""
"Null values still persist if the location of that null value does not "
"exist in `other`"
msgstr "如果该空值的位置在 `other` 中不存在，则空值仍然保留"

